{"tid":585777,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"社保基金盤數有幾惡劣？赤字7000億！","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T12:43:51.000Z","uid":30169,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0edeb01b774b703b7790b6af1c32cb41553704","tid":585777,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"【社保基金盤數有幾惡劣？赤字7000億！】<br />\n【政府不打救，三年半後退休保障全面崩潰】<br />\n樓繼偉是全國社保基金理事長，對社保基金的財政狀況了解最深，他在政協會議上提出警告，社保基金的保費已經入不敷支。「一些省份已經收不抵支，我們子孫輩將承受更大的負擔。」<br />\n究竟社保基金的財政狀況有多惡劣？由2013年中國勞動力由頂點萎縮開始，社保基本就一下子，由收支盈餘約800億，變成收支赤字2200億，到2017年，再跳升至7000億。<br />\n如果沒有政府的補貼，以社保基本現時大約2萬4千億結餘計算，就算未來幾年赤字維持在7000億不變，人口老化問題亦不會持續惡化，3年半後社保基金結餘就會完全枯竭。所以未來中央政府出手補貼，看來是無可避免。<br />\n#社保基金<br />\n#入不敷支<br />\n#樓繼偉<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1658376160973530/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1658376160973530%2F&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=6d007859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1658376160973530/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/112146_ab8b88dacf928ee385bc3b1ee7e1df2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F112146_ab8b88dacf928ee385bc3b1ee7e1df2c.png&h=404c68e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db475ff5bba3d99360b121fea1463d0cab39e0c5","tid":585777,"uid":62842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"共產黨咁樣搞 30年後仲存唔存在都難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7601fcc04ab0c78be0da8afb6ed3462f70cf82cb","tid":585777,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db475ff5bba3d99360b121fea1463d0cab39e0c5","tid":585777,"uid":62842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"201